replies.body:
Issues with the login screen not coming up are usually caused by your client not being able to establish a solid link to the login service. I recommend ensuring your local network settings are good by working through our [connection troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if these steps caused any change.
